title: #92Noon! Coping/VikingsTalkers/BirkBit/AndrewMiller
description: This is the "Coping Covenant." We are you. First hour includes the always-controversial "Stump the Snob" game featuring Meatsauce & Bossberg, Matt Birk on the hotline from his bunker, Vikings COO Andrew Miller with some perspective on how the Vikes are handling things in the present, Vikes talkers and more!
